Web Design
Wireframes - Drawing technique used to create the shapes and visual structure of a website.
Goals of the website
Website Elements
-image gallery (portfolio)
-About page
-Contact page
-Header
-Footer

Draw wireframes

for phones, tablets and desktop

Responsive Web Design
uses three technics
1. Create fluid images.  Use percentages in the css
2. Create a fluid grid.
3. A media query, based on the width of the page

